&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/kafka/pull/1824&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/kafka/pull/1824&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-4123&quot; title=&quot;Queryable State returning null for key before all stores in instance have been initialized&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;KAFKA-4123&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;KAFKA-4123&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: RocksDBStore can be marked as open before it has been initialized&lt;/p&gt;

